---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="FAQ — CalcKaro" description="Frequently Asked Questions about CalcKaro, India's Calculator Hub.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8 py-8">
    <div class="border-b border-vercel-gray-medium pb-4">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mt-2">Everything you need to know about CalcKaro.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">What is CalcKaro?</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
          CalcKaro is a specialized, fast, and free online calculator hub designed specifically for users in India. We focus on delivering precise, dynamic tools tailored to Indian taxation, compliance, and academic systems.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Why are the numbers formatted differently?</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
          All financial outputs on CalcKaro utilize the Indian numbering system (e.g. lakhs and crores, formatted as ₹1,50,000) rather than millions/billions. This reflects the standard invoicing and financial representation in India.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Are the calculations updated for the latest fiscal year?</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
          Yes! All tax calculators, salary deductions, HRA exemptions, and other compliance tools are updated in real-time to match the budgets and interest rates active for the current financial year (including FY 2025-26).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-2">
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-white">Is my data secure on CalcKaro?</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
          Absolutely. All calculation logic runs directly in your web browser (client-side execution). We do not send your financial inputs or personal values to any server, keeping your data 100% private.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
